Vagabond
The Vagabond is the ultimate survivor: a wanderer with no permanent home
and no fixed allegiance. They live by their wits, picking up skills wherever
life takes them across the shattered landscape of Rifts Earth.

Vagabonds have the most skill picks of any OCC, compensating for the lack of
focused training. They are adaptable generalists who can find their feet in
any situation: city, wilderness, or combat zone.

Attribute requirements: None. Any OCC-eligible race may choose Vagabond.
Starting equipment: Travelling clothes, backpack, survival knife, canteen,
rations, and one ranged weapon of choice.
